Class AbstractMoveableNervousSystemElement

java.lang.Object
prkmodel.types.templates.AbstractNervousSystemElement
prkmodel.types.templates.AbstractMoveableNervousSystemElement
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractCytokine
public abstract class AbstractMoveableNervousSystemElement extends AbstractNervousSystemElement implements MoveableNervousSystemElement
Abstract base class for moveable nervous system elements. Provides common functionality and properties for elements in the nervous system that can move.

To implement a subclass:

  • Ensure the constructor properly initializes inherited fields.
  • Override methods to provide specific behavior.
  • Document the purpose of any new methods or overridden methods.
  • Use super to call the superclass method when overriding to extend or modify its behavior.
